<parameter name="content"># Flour Power Hub - System Startup Guide

## Quick Start (3 Steps)

### Step 1: Start the Backend
```bash
cd backend
npm run dev
```
- Runs on port 3001
- Connects to PostgreSQL database

### Step 2: Build & Start Frontend (Production Mode)
```bash
# Build the frontend
npm run build

# Start preview server on port 8081
npm run preview -- --port 8081
```

### Step 3: Start Cloudflare Tunnel
```bash
cloudflared tunnel --config ~/.cloudflared/config.yml run
```

---

